      "missing_data": [],
      "script": "look-06-input-output-efficiency/scripts/look_06_input_output_efficiency.py",
      "test_status": "passed",
      "review_status": "reviewed",
      "notes": "分析营运资金/收入、固定资产/收入、人均投入产出，含行业基准对标。金融类公司不适用。已拆分为独立 skill：look-06-input-output-efficiency。"
    },
    {
